text:
Heh~, what about you, Producer~?
You seemed a bit off~

Well... Remember the cream puff you mentioned before,
Hinana? The limited-time one?

Oh~... Yeah,
the one that overlapped with the training camp~

I tried to figure out a way to get it somehow,
but it didn't work out in the end.

Oh~...!?
Producer, did you really want to eat it that badly~?
Well, it did look really delicious though~...

............
Wasn't Hinana that eager to eat it?

Not at all~
Hinana really wanted to eat it!

But you can't do anything about things
that are impossible, right~?

I see...
If Hinana's okay with it, then it's fine.
You were going to buy it for Hinana~?
...Haha, well, I ended up not being able to buy it after all.

RIght~... That's too bad.
Hinana wanted to eat it together with you~?
